By: Peter Sterry
---
The Spirit is the Fountain of Life, which flowes forth from God, to
Feed, and Maintain the Breath of Life in the Body. When the time of
Death comes, This Spirit draws back to their Head again Those streams
of Life, by which It went forth into the Body.
